cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM 

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with semantic road image segmentation using stereo images. It may also belong to the robotics (cs.RO) sub-category as understanding road scenes is important for autonomous driving. The use of a neural network for semantic segmentation suggests that it may also belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, the use of stereo images and disparity maps suggests that it may also belong to the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
